public abstract class QueryParameters
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

Contains common parameters for any kind of search: result type, page parameters and relationships to fetch automatically for entities.

The attribute fetch may contain a List of Relationships, identifying those which should be automatically loaded by the persistence mechanism. It provides an external way to lazily load such relationships whenever is necessary. For more information, see FetchService documentation.

Author:
luis
